            <div class="bg-amber-100 w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
              <i data-lucide="activity" class="text-amber-500 w-8 h-8"></i>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-4">專屬運動處方</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600 mb-8 flex-grow leading-relaxed">
              不知道怎麼開始運動？輸入基本資料，立刻為你打造專屬的階段性運動計畫。
            </p>
            <a href="https://smilecloud.tw/gogoexercise/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center text-sky-600 font-bold hover:text-sky-700 mt-auto">
              領取專屬處方 <i data-lucide="arrow-right" class="ml-2 w-5 h-5"></i>
            </a>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-sm border border-slate-100 hover:shadow-xl hover:border-sky-200 transition-all group flex flex-col h-full">
            <div class="bg-rose-100 w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
