      </div>
      <p class="mb-10 text-slate-300">讓專業知識走進家庭，陪伴孩子健康成長。</p>
      
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4 mb-12">
        <a href="https://www.facebook.com/share/1FoPpvVSZs/?mibextid=wwXIfr" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" class="flex items-center gap-2 bg-slate-800 hover:bg-blue-600 text-white px-8 py-3.5 rounded-full font-medium transition-all w-full sm:w-auto justify-center shadow-md">
